My toddler LOVES Super Why, and I actually don't feel bad about letting her watch it. She particularly likes the Hansel and Gretel episode, and wants to watch it over and over, which is great because it talks about healthy eating - eating a variety of things including fruits and vegetables, and talks about how eating too much candy and sugar is bad for us and makes us lose our energy. This has resonated with our daughter and she's LESS likely to want candy after watching Super Why. Not that it's eliminated candy, but at least it's positive reinforcement that she seems receptive to. She's also starting to recognize more letters. We are ordering more Super Why DVDs!
My order arrived fast and they were brand spanking new DVD's! My baby boy adores Super Why and I adore Amazon's great products and fast delivery. They make every order so fast n easy!
